    <tags>ram memory cleaner optimizer tray windows admin</tags>
    <summary>Lightweight Windows RAM cleaner — 163 KB static binary with system tray, hotkey, auto-clean, status window, and process exclusions.</summary>
    <description>RAMKeeper is a lightweight (163 KB) portable Windows RAM cleaner that purges the standby/cached memory list via NtSetSystemInformation, immediately reclaiming memory without rebooting.

## Features

- **System tray app** — runs quietly in the background
- **Status window** — left-click tray for color-coded RAM %, sparkline, clean history
- **Global hotkey** — Ctrl+Alt+R triggers an instant purge from anywhere
- **Auto-clean modes** — threshold-based, interval-based, idle-based, scheduled daily clean
- **Process exclusions** — skip specific exe names from working-set trim
- **No runtime dependencies** — single static binary, no .NET, no MSVC redistributable
- **No ads, no telemetry** — MIT licensed, open source

## Notes

RAMKeeper requires administrator privileges because the standby memory purge needs SeProfileSingleProcessPrivilege.

This is a portable executable. Chocolatey installs it to the tools directory and creates a shim so `RAMKeeper` is available from any terminal.
    </description>
